<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/51a2e97c576c4b8ea39935f7dae5ce2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>【齐心协力，共守大荒！全民参战解锁“剑心问道”主线！】</p>
